      "text": "私は負けません\nスリクスにも、サニピにも、どんなライバルにだって",
      "startTime": 151.5444401461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "あ、とんかつの匂い……",
      "startTime": 156.5444442151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことを言うのは、デリカシーがないと思います",
      "startTime": 161.2444279387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "まだ何も言ってないだろ！？",
      "startTime": 165.1777612721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "最近、ずっと気が張っていて食欲がなかったんです",
      "startTime": 167.2782148158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_03-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "でも、さくらととんかつを食べてからは\n今までの反動なのか、妙にお腹がすいちゃって……",
      "startTime": 175.2782148158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
